nebula changelog

1.0.3 (WIP)
  - (No real code change) Drop support for C++11 and CUDA <9.2; add support for modern versions of CUDA.

1.0.2 (2021-05-26)
  - Fix bug where only partial simulations were done when a low number of primaries are provided (GPU version).

1.0.1 (2021-02-16)
  - Add support for Windows (thanks Alexander Skorikov)
  - Support CUDA Toolkit 11 (thanks Alexander Skorikov)
  - Add upper energy bound to simulations

1.0.0 (2020-06-02)
  - Initial release
